snippet.title: New KungFuPunk ARPG game | Phantom Blade: Executioners
snippet.description:
Phantom Blade: Executioners is an action game proudly presented by S-Game. A dark epic of KUNGfUPUNK. Endless combat styles. Compromises and confrontations, Bring everything to an end in this fateful duel!

Official Website: https://pbex.s-gamestudio.com/
Official Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PBEXglobal/
Official Discord: https://discord.gg/Dc9Ns3BZsN
